		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/05/club-of-amsterdam.html" title="Permalink to Club of Amsterdam" rel="bookmark">Club of Amsterdam</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/05/club-of-amsterdam.html" title="16:01" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-05-05T16:01:39+00:00" pubdate>May 5, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/05/club-of-amsterdam.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Last week I had the pleas­ure of speak­ing at the <a href="http://www.clubofamsterdam.com/default.asp">Club of Ams­ter­dam</a>.  The topic under dis­cus­sion was “The future of digital iden­tity”.  Many thanks to Felix and the team. A lively even­ing.<br />
<iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/65163687" height="281" width="500" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>
<p><a href="http://vimeo.com/65163687">Annie Machon at the Club of Ams­ter­dam</a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/anniemachon">Annie Machon</a> on <a href="http://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.<br />
First pub­lished in my news­let­ter last week, amongst much else. Do sign up!</p>
