	<article id="post-164" class="post-164 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-big-brother category-civil-liberties category-democracy category-intelligence category-law category-machon category-mi5 category-mi6 category-national-security category-police category-politics category-spies category-surveillance category-talks-2 category-whistleblowers tag-annie-machon tag-big-brother tag-civil-liberties-2 tag-eth-0 tag-intelligence-2 tag-police-state tag-spies-2 tag-surveillance-2">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2010/05/talking-about-totalitarianism-at-eth0-january-2010.html" title="Permalink to Talking about totalitarianism at ETH-0, January 2010" rel="bookmark">Talking about totalitarianism at <span class="caps">ETH-0</span>, January 2010</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2010/05/talking-about-totalitarianism-at-eth0-january-2010.html" title="18:30" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2010-05-06T18:30:01+00:00" pubdate>May 6, 2010</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2010/05/talking-about-totalitarianism-at-eth0-january-2010.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p><a style="float: left;" href="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/6a00e5509030318833013482850b90970c-popup.html" onclick="window.open( this.href, '_blank', 'width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0' ); return false"><img  class="asset asset-image at-xid-6a00e5509030318833013482850b90970c " alt="ETH-0_Poster" src="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/6a00e5509030318833013482850b90970c-120wi.jpg" style="margin: 0px 5px 5px 0px;" /></a>In Janu­ary I had the pleas­ure of speak­ing in The Neth­er­lands at the excel­lent geek­fest known as <span class="caps">ETH-0</span>.  Rather than just banging on about the spooks, I thought it was time to take a step back and exam­ine what exactly we mean when we talk about total­it­ari­an­ism, police states, and how far down the road our coun­tries have gone.</p>
<p> I also wanted to drive home to an audi­ence, many of whom are too young to remem­ber the Cold War, what exactly it would be like to live under a police state with its endemic surveillance.  </p>
</p>
<p>And here’s the talk:</p>
<p class="asset asset-video" style="display: block; margin: 0pt auto;" align="center"><object type="application/x-shockwave-flash" data="http://vimeo.com/moogaloop.swf" height="200" width="352"><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true"><param name="movie" value="http://vimeo.com/moogaloop.swf"><param name="flashvars" value="clip_id=13708192&#038;color=00adef&#038;fullscreen=1&#038;server=vimeo.com&#038;show_byline=1&#038;show_portrait=1&#038;show_title=1"></object></p>
<p></p></p>
</p>					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
